ChangeLog
================================================================================

This file is generated from svn log for informational purposes only and thus 
might not always be up to date. Use the svn log command to get a more recent 
list of changes.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r27 | ionflux | 2006-12-04 22:05:40 +0100 (Mo, 04 Dez 2006) | 14 lines

+ IFExampleClass: Added a test application; changed namespace 
  declarations in the implementation.
+ Class templates: Changed to use new enum IFVerbosityLevel instead 
  of IFLogMessage member constants; some changes to the way namespaces 
  are used in the implementation of events and signal proxies.
+ Added a new logging API which is suitable for global functions and 
  supports a default logging target; Moved declaration of verbosity 
  levels from IFLogMessage member constants to enum IFVerbosityLevel.
+ Added UTF-8 encoder/decoder functions.
+ IFObject: Added an API to create a literal from an object and 
  restore the persistent state from a literal.
+ Updated all classes from updated class templates.
+ Updated TODO list.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r26 | ionflux | 2006-12-03 17:26:27 +0100 (So, 03 Dez 2006) | 7 lines

+ IFExampleClass: Added examples for serialization and operations; 
  Moved the code to the test directory.
+ Class templates: Added fully qualified names for some 
  Ionflux::ObjectBase types (this should be checked again, 
  thoroughly).
+ Updated TODO list.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
