r16 | ionflux | 2006-09-26 22:32:47 +0200 (Di, 26 Sep 2006) | 11 lines

+ Added configuration and autogenerated implementation for IFSignal, 
  IFGuard and IFLogMessage.
+ Class templates: Features are now checked uniformly in a dedicated 
  section across the header and implementation templates; class info 
  is now a feature which is activated either for IFObject derived 
