+ Added main configuration file for example class and associated 
  events.
+ IFExampleClass.conf: Updated to support new features.
+ Added configuration for IFObject (to be reviewed thoroughly).
+ Added automatically generated class files (which probably will not 
  compile - more cleanup/testing is required and some classes are 
  missing; see TODO).

